        Creates a GameStepPlayer with the given values.
        Parameters:
        playerId - unique id of the player
        active - shows if the player is alive
        direction - direction the player is currently moving in
        speed - current speed the player is moving with
        position - position as Point2i of the player on the Board
        round - round the information is valid for
